<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 May 2024 02:24:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡还能抵御提前选举和加沙战略吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/can-netanyahu-still-fend-off-early-elections-and-a-strategy-for-gaza/0000018f-8d4b-d926-a18f-edcf2da80000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁伙伴约夫·加兰特和本尼·甘茨现在都对他投了不信任票。但甘茨发表了相当懦弱的演讲，总理根本没有兴趣解雇他</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 20:06:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/can-netanyahu-still-fend-off-early-elections-and-a-strategy-for-gaza/0000018f-8d4b-d926-a18f-edcf2da80000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨要求在6月8日之前制定战后加沙计划，否则他将辞去内塔尼亚胡政府职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/gantz-demands-post-war-gaza-plan-by-june-8-or-he-will-quit-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-8d03-ded1-a7df-dd5319040000</link><description>战时内阁部长在新闻发布会上表示，“个人和政治考虑已进入以色列国防最神圣的部分”，并呼吁内塔尼亚胡总理“做正确的事”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 19:41:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/gantz-demands-post-war-gaza-plan-by-june-8-or-he-will-quit-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-8d03-ded1-a7df-dd5319040000</guid></item><item><title>人质罗恩·本亚明的尸体从加沙地带运回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/body-of-hostage-ron-binyamin-retrieved-to-israel-from-gaza/0000018f-8ca0-d9d6-a38f-8dfb43e10000</link><description>以色列军方宣布，53 岁的本亚明 (Binyamin) 的尸体于周五与人质沙尼·洛克 (Shani Louk)、阿米特·布斯基拉 (Amit Buskila) 和伊扎克·格勒伦特 (Itzhak Gelerenter) 一起被打捞上岸。他是两个孩子的父亲，自 10 月 7 日以来命运未卜。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 17:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/body-of-hostage-ron-binyamin-retrieved-to-israel-from-gaza/0000018f-8ca0-d9d6-a38f-8dfb43e10000</guid></item><item><title>当无人谈论时，她领导了争取妇女和 LGBTQ 权利的斗争：Yael Dayan 是一位泰坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/she-fought-for-womens-and-lgbtq-rights-when-no-one-else-was-yael-dayan-was-a-titan/0000018f-8c91-d7a5-abcf-8dbb32a70000</link><description>即使在生病之后，达扬仍然是一位忠实的公众人物，她可怕的疾病成为她处理的另一个问题。她无所畏惧，抚养了一代年轻人，他们将在这里建立一个模范社会</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 17:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/she-fought-for-womens-and-lgbtq-rights-when-no-one-else-was-yael-dayan-was-a-titan/0000018f-8c91-d7a5-abcf-8dbb32a70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第225天：外国消息人士称，停战谈判陷入“僵局”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-225-truce-talks-are-at-an-impasse-foreign-source-says/0000018f-8c7e-d9d6-a38f-8dffd6100000</link><description>一位熟悉谈判的外国消息人士告诉《国土报》，以色列和哈马斯之间的停战谈判“没有取得任何进展”。 ■ 白宫表示，以色列愿意在就拉法的广泛军事行动做出重大决定之前继续进行谈判。组建“人道主义卫队”，保护援助车队免受以色列极右活动分子的袭击 ■ 战争进入 225 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 16:40:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-225-truce-talks-are-at-an-impasse-foreign-source-says/0000018f-8c7e-d9d6-a38f-8dffd6100000</guid></item><item><title>反对党领袖拉皮德呼吁甘茨和艾森科特离开政府，以色列各地数千人举行抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/hostage-release-and-anti-government-protests-to-be-held-across-israel-on-saturday-night/0000018f-8c17-d273-a1af-aed7e2800000</link><description>数十名反政府抗议者封锁了特拉维夫的阿亚隆高速公路，美国大使在特拉维夫的人质集会上发表讲话。周一，在议会夏季会议开幕之前，抗议车队前往耶路撒冷</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 15:33:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/hostage-release-and-anti-government-protests-to-be-held-across-israel-on-saturday-night/0000018f-8c17-d273-a1af-aed7e2800000</guid></item><item><title>定居者袭击了他们认为正在向加沙运送援助物资的巴勒斯坦卡车司机以及前来治疗他的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/settlers-attack-trucker-thought-to-be-delivering-aid-to-gaza-and-soldiers-who-helped-him/0000018f-8687-d443-adef-9fcf68460000</link><description>在最近一次定居者反对向加沙运送人道主义援助的暴力抗议中，一辆卡车被迫停在科恰夫·哈沙哈尔定居点附近并被焚烧，导致司机中度受伤，三名前来援助他的以色列国防军士兵受轻伤。没有逮捕任何人</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 14:35:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/settlers-attack-trucker-thought-to-be-delivering-aid-to-gaza-and-soldiers-who-helped-him/0000018f-8687-d443-adef-9fcf68460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部被警察枪杀的贝都因妇女称她无缘无故被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-shot-by-police-officer-in-southern-israel-says-she-was-shot-for-no-reason/0000018f-8b12-ded1-a7df-df520b880000</link><description>伊塔布·阿萨娜 (Itab A-Sana) 的腿部被一名前来搜寻她儿子的警察开枪射中，她的儿子目前正在接受审讯。警方表示，这名警官向一只狗开枪，他认为这只狗构成危险，阿萨娜受伤后警方呼吁医疗救助</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 13:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-shot-by-police-officer-in-southern-israel-says-she-was-shot-for-no-reason/0000018f-8b12-ded1-a7df-df520b880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前议员、自由派偶像雅埃尔·达扬 (Yael Dayan) 去世，享年 85 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/yael-dayan-former-israeli-lawmaker-and-liberal-icon-dies-at-85/0000018e-c3ab-dc93-adce-effbd4580000</link><description>达扬 (Dayan) 于 1992 年至 2003 年间担任以色列议会议员，是一位著名的人权活动家，关注妇女和 LGBTQ 群体的问题。近年来，她患有严重的肺部疾病</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 12:20:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/yael-dayan-former-israeli-lawmaker-and-liberal-icon-dies-at-85/0000018e-c3ab-dc93-adce-effbd4580000</guid></item><item><title>第一批救援卡车通过新开放的浮动码头进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/first-convoy-of-aid-trucks-cross-into-gaza-via-newly-opened-floating-pier/0000018f-8b1e-d6b6-a59f-fb9fb4bc0000</link><description>美国官员预计该行动每天将运送 150 卡车的援助物资，然后由联合国世界粮食计划署收集和分发</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 11:49:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/first-convoy-of-aid-trucks-cross-into-gaza-via-newly-opened-floating-pier/0000018f-8b1e-d6b6-a59f-fb9fb4bc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议员纳马·拉齐米并不害怕内塔尼亚胡和本·格维尔。她会带回犹太复国主义左翼吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-and-ben-gvir-dont-scare-israeli-mk-naama-lazimi-can-she-save-the-zionist-left/0000018f-8649-d7ca-afcf-97eb622d0000</link><description>近几个月来，工党议员纳马·拉齐米 (Naama Lazimi) 一直是反政府抗议活动前线的重要人物，与人质家属并肩作战，争取亲人从加沙返回。她说：“我是议会反对党成员，我有责任尽我所能控制警察并团结一致。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 10:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-and-ben-gvir-dont-scare-israeli-mk-naama-lazimi-can-she-save-the-zionist-left/0000018f-8649-d7ca-afcf-97eb622d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军和辛贝特在加沙地带找到了哈马斯扣押的三名以色列人质的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</link><description>沙尼·洛克、阿米特·布斯基拉和伊扎克·格勒伦特都被新星狂欢节劫持为人质。据以色列国防军称，三人从狂欢场跑到梅法西姆交界处，在那里被哈马斯恐怖分子谋杀，尸体被带入加沙</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 08:47:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-retrieves-bodies-of-three-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas-in-gaza-strip/0000018f-875c-d7f9-a5ff-b77eecc40000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯犹太运动“站在一起”计划保护加沙援助车队免受右翼掠夺者的侵害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/arab-jewish-movement-standing-together-to-guard-gaza-aid-convoys-from-right-wing-looters/0000018f-8a88-d9d6-a38f-8ffb2bc10000</link><description>为了抵制右翼活动人士阻止援助卡车抵达加沙的努力，“站在一起”计划建立一个缓冲区，并希望警方帮助维持和平</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 08:13:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/arab-jewish-movement-standing-together-to-guard-gaza-aid-convoys-from-right-wing-looters/0000018f-8a88-d9d6-a38f-8ffb2bc10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可能会跌倒并再次崛起</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-may-fall-and-rise-again/0000018f-89d3-d7f4-adbf-a9ff75c10000</link><description>那些谈论以色列灭亡的人可以分为两类：希望以色列灭亡的人和害怕以色列灭亡的人。以色列人未来可能会失去主权——但这可能不是我们想象的噩梦</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 04:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/israel-may-fall-and-rise-again/0000018f-89d3-d7f4-adbf-a9ff75c10000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸的 18 个巴勒斯坦牧羊社区最近被消灭。这个可能是下一个</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/18-west-bank-shepherding-communities-have-been-recently-erased-this-one-might-be-next/0000018f-83c5-d9d6-a38f-87ff376b0000</link><description>定居者多年来一直骚扰杰里科附近的一个贝都因小村庄，但在战争期间，他们加大了恐吓力度。身着军服、配备军车的大屠杀分子夺取了该地区的土地，并建立了 13 个新的前哨基地——这一切都是从 10 月份开始的</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:50:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/18-west-bank-shepherding-communities-have-been-recently-erased-this-one-might-be-next/0000018f-83c5-d9d6-a38f-87ff376b0000</guid></item><item><title>“犯罪组织正在控制以色列的阿拉伯社会。他们也是为了犹太社会而来”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/crime-orgs-are-controlling-israels-arab-society-theyre-coming-for-jewish-society-too/0000018f-8990-d9d6-a38f-8dfb38780000</link><description>Rawyah Handaqlu 是一个紧急机构的负责人，该机构的成立是为了应对席卷阿拉伯社会的犯罪和暴力浪潮，他谈论了生活在一个犯罪组织取代国家的社会中的感受</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 03:27:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/crime-orgs-are-controlling-israels-arab-society-theyre-coming-for-jewish-society-too/0000018f-8990-d9d6-a38f-8dfb38780000</guid></item><item><title>“我们的鲜血只适合战争”：在加沙作战，埃塞俄比亚以色列人感到平等。回到家，这种感觉就破碎了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/fighting-in-gaza-they-feel-equal-back-home-in-israel-that-feeling-is-shattered/0000018f-870e-d443-adef-9fce5c9d0000</link><description>在加沙服役和阵亡的以色列士兵中有相当多的埃塞俄比亚人后裔。有些人认为战争已经成为进入以色列社会的一种门票——但代价是什么？</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 02:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/fighting-in-gaza-they-feel-equal-back-home-in-israel-that-feeling-is-shattered/0000018f-870e-d443-adef-9fce5c9d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在拉法部署另一个旅，估计有80万巴勒斯坦人离开该市</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-live/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-wanted-terrorist-killed/0000018f-8960-d9d6-a38f-8dfb3ff10000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：甘茨设定的条件是以色列失败的委婉说法。 ■ 以色列国防军称，人质罗恩·本亚明的尸体从加沙被打捞出来。 ■ 以色列国防军估计，自以色列进攻以来，近 80 万巴勒斯坦人撤离拉法。以色列军方称，从加沙北部向以色列南部发射了 10 枚火箭弹</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 May 2024 02:10:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article-live/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-wanted-terrorist-killed/0000018f-8960-d9d6-a38f-8dfb3ff10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空军袭击约旦河西岸的建筑物；杀死通缉恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-kills-wanted-terrorist/0000018f-88b3-d9d6-a38f-8dfb69480000</link><description>据以色列军方称，目标建筑被用作作战作战室</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:56:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-air-force-strikes-building-in-west-bank-kills-wanted-terrorist/0000018f-88b3-d9d6-a38f-8dfb69480000</guid></item><item><title>加州大学武装警察与亲巴勒斯坦抗议者发生暴力冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/armed-police-clash-violently-with-pro-palestinian-protesters-at-california-university/0000018f-8898-d9d6-a38f-8dfbee7e0000</link><description>加州大学欧文分校的亲巴勒斯坦营地占领了一座空置建筑，导致警方采取严厉措施，近 50 人被捕</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-18/ty-article/.premium/armed-police-clash-violently-with-pro-palestinian-protesters-at-california-university/0000018f-8898-d9d6-a38f-8dfbee7e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>